  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>If you need information on something, you know if there is a book containing that information and where to find it.</p><p>Further, when you hear a creature speaking or when you see language written down, you can identify exactly what language is being used even if you are not proficient in the language.</p><p>Finally, when you hear music, you know which instruments are being used in the performance, even if you are not proficient in their use.</p>",
